据评论汇总网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]统计，游戏所获评价“两级或中庸”<ref>{{Cite web |title=LBX: Little Battlers eXperience |url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/3ds/lbx-little-battlers-experience |access-date=2022-04-29 |website=Metacritic |language=en}}</ref>。

任天堂世界报道的Donald Thierault称，《爆Boost》紧紧抓住了[[宝可梦系列|宝可梦系列]]风格公式，表面简单但后期很有深度<ref>{{Cite web |last=Thierault |first=Donald |date=2015-09-08 |title=LBX: Little Battlers eXperience Review - Review |url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/review/41110/lbx-little-battlers-experience-3ds-review |access-date=2022-04-29 |website=Nintendo World Report}}</ref>。RPGamer的Alex Fuller批评游戏故事单薄、糟糕至极，虽然作品总体很好玩，却没有发挥潜力<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |last=Fuller |first=Alex |title=LBX: Little Battlers eXperience Review |url=https://rpgamer.com/review/lbx-little-battlers-experience-review/ |access-date=2022-05-01 |website=RPGamer |language=en-US}}</ref>。

